7 years ago","ctime":"April 5 2010, 13:26:48 UTC","parent":9581746,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: Get Lost...","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"werthead","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"werthead","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"werthead","ctime_ts":"1270474008","tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/51443191/3030116","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?replyto=9582002","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9582002#t9582002","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9582002#t9582002","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9582002#t9582002","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"hippoiathanatoi","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://hippoiathanatoi.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":9582002,"talkid":37429,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9582002#t9582002","upictitle":"Elio &amp; Linda: Elio","article":"Interesting list. Of the best novels, Valente's is my personal favorite (how weird is it that <span  class=\"ljuser  i-ljuser  i-ljuser-deleted  i-ljuser-type-P     \"  data-ljuser=\"antipope\" lj:user=\"antipope\" ><a href=\"http://antipope.livejournal.com/profile\"  target=\"_self\"  class=\"i-ljuser-profile\" ><img  class=\"i-ljuser-userhead\"  src=\"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10\" /></a><a href=\"http://antipope.livejournal.com/\" class=\"i-ljuser-username\"   target=\"_self\"   ><b>antipope</b></a></span> had a story by the same title in the novella category? Never seen that weird sort of synchronicity before). Simply gorgeous. That said, I suspect Valente's (and Bacigalupi's) are outside shots at winning. I'm thinking this may be Mi√©ville's year.<br /><br />Pleased that <em>This is Me, Jack Vance!</em> is on best related, but it seems to me it's probably more a sentimental choice than anything -- Vance is a wonderful character, and I enjoyed reading the book for what it was, a narrativeless series of amusing or interesting vignettes more-or-less chronologically in order. It seems to me Vance and Clute are frontrunners at this stage, though, just based on name recognition and importance in the field (Mendelsohn is collecting a really extensive body of critical work, though, so who knows...)<br /><br />A whole lot of Dr. Who in the Dramatic Short category. I'm cheering for \"Epitaph One\", but I suspect it' all but certain to be the good doctor's day (yet again).","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"April 4 2010, 23:48:58 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://hippoiathanatoi.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"hippoiathanatoi","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"hippoiathanatoi","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://hippoiathanatoi.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"hippoiathanatoi","ctime_ts":"1270424938","tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/51869646/10680603","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?replyto=9588914","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9588914#t9588914","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9588914#t9588914","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9588914#t9588914","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"vandersock","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://vandersock.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":9588914,"talkid":37456,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9588914#t9588914","above":9582002,"upictitle":"Herr Van der Sock: lol kitty","article":"I think Valente's novel is fairly polarizing: it is (unfortunately) the only one of the novel nominees I've managed to read, and I disliked it profoundly and heartily, and it seems to me to be the kind of book that will provoke those reactions.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"April 5 2010, 18:54:37 UTC","parent":9582002,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://vandersock.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"vandersock","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"vandersock","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://vandersock.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"vandersock","ctime_ts":"1270493677","tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/51443191/3030116","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?replyto=9591474","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9591474#t9591474","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/145074.html?thread=9591474#t9591474","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"all